      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_8590036913100408602.png",
                "id": "talent96349",
                "key": "Spiritfox Sin-Eater",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Spiritfox Sin-Eater"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Memanggil <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Sesshou Sakura</span>. Jika awalnya sudah ada di arena, maka <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Sesshou Sakura</span> akan mengakibatkan DMG +1 tambahan. (Maksimum +1)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/7e9f291d99b3519d86302e803782b2f7_3927274237078197268.png",
                "id": "talent13658",
                "key": "Yakan Evocation: Sesshou Sakura",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Yakan Evocation: Sesshou Sakura"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 4 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span>; Jika kamu punya<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> Sesshou Sakura</span> di arena, maka akan dihancurkan lalu menciptakan <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Tenko Thunderbolt</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Tenko Thunderbolt</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status Pertempuran</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Sebelum kamu memilih Aksi-mu:</span> Mengakibatkan 3 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan: 1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/56f64a44b1ccee62527e2a18a46de27f_496705652903041619.png",
                "id": "talent90064",
                "key": "Great Secret Art: Tenko Kenshin",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Great Secret Art: Tenko Kenshin"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Panggilan</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Tahap Selesai:</span> Mengakibatkan 1 <span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">Electro DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Penggunaan: 3</span> (Dapat ditumpuk, maksimum 6 tumpukan)</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Saat kamu mengakhiri ronde:</span> Jika <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Penggunaan</span> kartu ini 4 atau lebih, mengakibatkan 1 poin Electro DMG. (Mengonsumsi Penggunaan)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_1914295137743092790.png",
                "id": "talent70085",
                "key": "Sesshou Sakura",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/9935fc2ef27a255d96756090578adee7_811188714070033625.png",
                "title": "Sesshou Sakura"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Memberikan Electro dan dapat memicu Reaksi Elemental berikut:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini, target berganti ke Karakter selanjutnya secara paksa</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, mengakibatkan 1 Piercing DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, mengakibatkan 1 Piercing DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, menciptakan [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] yang memberikan +1 poin DMG ke 2 kasus Dendro DMG atau Electro DMG berikutnya</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_5701060138831822031.png",
                "id": "talent31911",
                "key": "Electro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Electro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Penggunaan</span></strong></p><p>Setelah efek kartu ini dipicu, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span>-nya akan dikonsumsi.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah semua <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span> telah dikonsumsi.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_8523128662528824601.png",
